{"tid":1464470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要攬抄 仲要理班鬼佬上唔上到機","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:04:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:13:05.000Z","uid":265133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2d42859a9243eb8633e5c03315c5bf58aec5662a","tid":1464470,"uid":265133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:04:38.000Z","msg":"我上次去遊行 係港鐵站有個鬼佬遊客一野撞埋黎仲用英文fuck我 <span style=\"color: red;\">唔關佢事佢未必理 正外我地好少理其他地區亂一樣<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n外國人要支持既人一早就支持 要出手一早就出手<br />\n藍絲話有外國勢力你都笑鳩佢啦<br />\n<br />\n外國出下聲就當幫忙 世界任何一個政府無利益都唔會出手 咪天真人地救你 自己香港自己救<br />\n<br />\n阻到班鬼佬上機 你咪叫自己國家發旅遊警示 有助攬炒 <br />\n<br />\n依加係要攬炒呀 唔係叫你表示和平一面 要實質幫一早已經幫 甘重視和平形象 真心聽警方呼籲 咪出街<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你可以和理非 人地亦可以行動派 除非亂甘打人 唔係一率不分不割</span>please"},{"pid":"6a3e42f845fd7dde7913c1ab50d8f01d40e4bff1","tid":1464470,"uid":76609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:05:20.000Z","msg":"block"},{"pid":"d68b5ea642c9c71bb70efcd8a2d8432811f144a3","tid":1464470,"uid":298077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:06:20.000Z","msg":"自己香港自己救 救得個公安 機場大把喬裝緊嘅popo如果再搵佢出嚟嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就大大力錫佢春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ee1a846fa4dfdc086ef0522d7057c57bb81155","tid":1464470,"uid":294974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:07:30.000Z","msg":"想公關係做好d將隻鑊射埋俾政府啫<br />\n<br />\n===============<br />\n入機場手足可以睇睇，如果覺得講得啱，唔該幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<br />\n<a h